Symptoms of Depression  
1.Feelings of sadness, emptiness or hopelessness
2.Angry outbursts, irritability or frustration, even over small matters
3.Sleep disturbances
4.Tiredness and lack of energy
5.Reduced appetite and weight loss 
6.Anxiety, agitation 
#depression #depressed

The delight of happy laughter,
The delight of peaceful days.
